<p data-index="1736">At January 31, 2020, Venden records an accounts payable to recognize its estimated additional liability to Amaya for expected future returns. The Estimated Inventory Returns account will generally be added to the Returned Inventory account at the end of the reporting period to identify returned and estimated inventory returns.</p>
