<p data-index="2077"><span class="center un" data-index="2078">(Consignor)</span></p></td>
<td colspan="3" style=" vertical-align: bottom;" data-index="2079">
<p data-index="2080"><span class="center" data-index="2081">Best Value Stores</span></p>
