<p data-index="4785">At the end of 2021, Construction in Process has a balance of $2,859,750 as shown in <a class="blue" href="#c18-fig-0051" id="c18-fig-0051-1" data-index="4786" data-section-index="28" data-section-idref="c18-fig-0051" data-target-data-index="4790"><b data-index="4787">Illustration 18A.19</b></a>.<a id="c18-note-1020" href="#c18-note-1020-a" data-index="4788" data-section-index="28" data-section-idref="c18-note-1020-a" data-target-data-index="7949"><sup data-index="4789">20</sup></a></p>
