</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<figcaption data-index="5102"><p data-index="5103"><span class="figureLabel" data-index="5104"><b data-index="5105"><a role="doc-backlink" href="#c18-fig-0053-1" data-index="5106" data-section-index="28" data-section-idref="c18-fig-0053-1" data-target-data-index="5002"><span style=" background-color: #226C7B; color: #FFFFFF;" data-index="5107">ILLUSTRATION 18B.2</span></a> Franchise Entries—Inception and Commencement of Operations</b></span></p></figcaption>
