<p class="latin1" id="c18-ex-0243" data-index="7129"><span class="label" data-index="7130"><b data-index="7131">b.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> Using the completed-contract method, compute the estimated gross profit that would be recognized during each year of the construction period.</p>
